Class AccountRegistration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.einarsandberg.projekt.AccountRegistration.AccountRegistration

  • public class AccountRegistration
extends java.lang.Object
    Create the correct account, given the accountType (user or admin). If any of the input fields is wrong, an account won't be created. Instead, a toast consisting of the wrong input field(s) will be displayed.
